.TH lexicon 1  "lexicon 0.1.0" 
.SH NAME
lexicon \- Lexicon Markdown processor for legal contracts
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBlexicon\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Lexicon Markdown processor for legal contracts
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
lexicon\-build(1)
Build a .docx from a Lexicon Markdown file
.TP
lexicon\-validate(1)
Validate a Lexicon Markdown file without generating output
.TP
lexicon\-man(1)
Generate man pages to a directory
.TP
lexicon\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH VERSION
v0.1.0
